title: >>> It all BEGINS AGAIN
body_text:
Before getting into the DODGEBALL XXX-ONE preview, perhaps an advanced schedule* of upcoming events would be of some help.
Saturday, 03/18/06 ~ DODGEBALL XXX-ONE
Saturday, 03/25/06 ~ DODGEBALL 32
Saturday, 04/01/06 ~ DODGEBALL 33
Saturday, 04/08/06 ~ DODGEBALL 34
Sunday, 04/16/06 ~ DODGEBALL 35 (Ocean Road Park with 3PM Start Time)
*All events subject to change*
Mark these dates on your calendars.
________________________________________
______________________
In "Season 3", unpredictability seemed to have been the standout word. Events 23 and XXIV are prime examples of how the weather wasn't as bad as it should have been this time of year. On the contrary, TWENTY-TWO, XXV, TWENTY-SIX, and even 30 were all "Wet Wars".
Attendances also saw a slip, but also reached new heights in the past two and a half months. January saw a decline with each passing event, February was arguably the most inconsistent month ever, yet has led March into what could be a "new beginning".
What is your prediction for DODGEBALL XXX-ONE?
To help you out, the attendance chart from events 1 through 30 is shown below.
It is hard to believe that dodgeball has be running wild for sixth months now. What can we expect at DODGEBALL XXX-ONE? The only sure way to know is to be there live on March 18th! The fourth "season" kicks off at its normal time of 7PM. The site for XXX-ONE is Wall High School.
As per a special bonus, click the link below and receive a gift!
